},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/wjX2Te0iZZ8GyQXcPjbyDSyH6AB.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/tyl2NSPii0ellGDY8nfolxbP68d.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/wxYYL8hQfCTNIxm3ZkPzbFW7vXM.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/ct3sRqWO9mulUfoAqC9LytgbVLW.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/swhEJGItE1S9mDTIZCB1z4z6026.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-04-21T08:15:27.97+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"Along with the Gods: The Two Worlds","runtime":139,"tagline":"Fate continues even after death.","homepage":"","overview":"Having died unexpectedly, firefighter Ja-hong is taken to the afterlife by 3 afterlife guardians. Only when he passes 7 trials over 49 days and proves he was innocent in human life, he’s able to reincarnate, and his 3 afterlife guardians are by his side to defend him in trial."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":139,"tagline":"누구나 가지만 아무도 본 적 없는 곳, 새로운 세계의 문이 열린다!","homepage":"","overview":"살인, 나태, 거짓, 불의, 배신, 폭력, 천륜 7개의 지옥에서 7번의 재판을 무사히 통과한 망자만이 환생하여 새로운 삶을 시작할 수 있다. 화재 사고 현장에서 여자아이를 구하고 죽음을 맞이한 소방관 자홍, 그의 앞에 저승차사 해원맥과 덕춘이 나타난다. 자신의 죽음이 아직 믿기지도 않는데 덕춘은 정의로운 망자이자 귀인이라며 그를 치켜세운다. 저승으로 가는 입구, 초군문에서 그를 기다리는 또 한 명의 차사 강림, 그는 차사들의 리더이자 앞으로 자홍이 겪어야 할 7개의 재판에서 변호를 맡아줄 변호사이기도 하다. 염라대왕에게 천년 동안 49명의 망자를 환생시키면 자신들 역시 인간으로 환생시켜 주겠다는 약속을 받은 삼차사들, 그들은 자신들이 변호하고 호위해야 하는 48번째 망자이자 19년 만에 나타난 의로운 귀인 자홍의 환생을 확신하지만, 각 지옥에서 자홍의 과거가 하나 둘씩 드러나면서 예상치 못한 고난과 맞닥뜨리는데…"},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"Along with the Gods: The Two Worlds","runtime":139,"tagline":"Le destin continue même après la mort","homepage":"","overview":"Après la mort d'une personne, un ange escorte le défunt dans l'au-delà où il doit être jugé sept fois durant 49 jours pour prouver qu'il a mené une vie humaine innocente et avoir le droit de se réincarner. Les anges ont l’interdiction absolue de se mêler des affaires humaines. Kim Ja-hong, un pompier mort de manière soudaine durant son travail, reçoit ainsi la visite de trois anges qui l'emmènent dans son voyage dans l'au-delà. L'un d'eux, Kang-rim, a cependant une affection pour les humains et désire l'aider plus qu'il n'en a le droit."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"与神同行：罪与罚","runtime":139,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"阴间有法，所有亡者在死后的49天内都要经过七次审判——分别在杀人狱、懒惰狱、欺骗狱、不义狱、背叛狱、暴力狱、天伦狱中进行，只有通过了七次审判宣告无罪的亡者，才有获得新生的机会。消防员金子洪在一场火灾当中为了救一名女孩而不幸牺牲。地狱使者解怨脉和德春出现在了金子洪的面前。尽管金子洪无法相信自己的死亡，却被德春一脸严肃地告知自己既是亡者、又是贵人。在通往地狱的入口，金子洪遇到了在初军门等着自己的另一位使者江林。他掌管着解怨脉和德春两位使者，同时也将在子洪即将接受的七次审判中为子洪进行辩护..."},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"與神同行","runtime":140,"tagline":"一個你不曾見過的世界","homepage":"","overview":"金自鴻是個正直又盡責的消防員，卻為了拯救一個小女孩而葬身火窟。來自地府的三位陰間使者出現在他面前，指引他通往死後的世界。這三位陰間使者分別是：「領袖」江林公子、「護衛」解怨脈、「助手」李德春。作為19年來的第一位「模範死者」，他們告訴金自鴻，如果想要「轉世」，他就必須在七七四十九天之內，通過七場審判。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"С Богами: Два мира","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Спасая ребёнка из горящего здания, пожарный Ким Джа-хон погибает героической смертью. И тут же три ангела смерти сопровождают его в мир мёртвых, где смертному предстоит пройти 7 судов и держать ответ перед 7-ю Богами. Ангелы будут его защитниками, и если Джа-хона признают безгрешным, он получит возможность реинкарнироваться и начать новую жизнь."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"Tanrı ile Günah ve Cezaya: İki Dünya","runtime":139,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Beklenmedik bir şekilde ölen itfaiyeci Ja-hong, üç öbür dünya gardiyanı tarafından ahirete götürülür. Ja-hong,  insan hayatında masum olduğunu kanıtlayıp, reenkarne olabilmek için ahirette gardiyanların eşliğinde 49 gün boyunca sürecek yedi mahkemeden geçecektir."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"Ανάμεσα στους Θεούς: Οι Δύο Κόσμοι","runtime":0,"tagline":"Η μοίρα συνεχίζεται ακόμα και μετά τον θάνατο","homepage":"","overview":"Μετά τον θάνατο ένας πυροσβέστης περιηγείται στη μετά θάνατον ζωή. Oπου εκεί θα έχει πολλές δοκιμασίες για να μάθει πως ζούσε και που έπρεπε πραγματικά να είναι."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"Along With the Gods: The Two Worlds","runtime":0,"tagline":"Osud pokračuje i po smrti","homepage":"","overview":"Po neočekávaném úmrtí je hasič Ja-hong přijat do posmrtného života třemi posmrtnými poslanci. Teprve když projde kolem sedmi zkoušek za 49 dnů a prokáže, že je v lidském životě nevinný, je schopen se reinkarnovat a jeho tři poslanci po skončení života jsou vedle něj, aby ho obhájili u soudu."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"ฝ่า 7 นรกไปกับพระเจ้า","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"ครั้งแรกที่ภาพของดินแดนปรโลกจะปรากฏต่อหน้าเราทุกคน เตรียมตัวออกผจญภัยฝ่านรกทั้ง7 ขุมที่จะไม่ได้เป็นแค่ภาพในจินตนาการ  ไปกับ 3 ยมทูตนักสู้ เพื่อส่งสุดยอดวิญญาณของนักดับเพลิงหนุ่มไปเกิดใหม่ให้สำเร็จ ในภาพยนตร์แอคชั่น-แฟนตาซีฟอร์มยักษ์ที่สร้างจากเว็บคอมมิคส์พันล้านวิวของเกาหลี"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"Along with the Gods: The Two Worlds","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ein Todesengel begleitet den Verstorbenen nach seinem Tod ins Jenseits. Dort hat die verstorbene Person 7 Gerichtsverfahren über einen Zeitraum von 49 Tagen. Der Todesengel, der sich nicht in menschliche Angelegenheiten einmischen soll, nimmt zu dieser Zeit unausweichlich an menschlichen Angelegenheiten teil."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Заједно са боговима: Два света","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Након што је умро изненада, Ја-хонг је одведен у загробни живот од стране три чувара. Једино када прође седам суђења која трају 49 дана, и докаже да је био невин у људском животу, биће способан да се реинкарнира. Његова три чувара на његовој су страни током суђења..."},"name":"Srpski","iso_639_1":"sr","iso_3166_1":"RS","english_name":"Serbian"},{"data":{"title":"Среща с Боговете: Двата свята","runtime":139,"tagline":"След смъртта на човек, Ангел на смъртта придружава починалия до отвъдния свят…","homepage":"","overview":"Филмът разказва историята на пожарникаря Ким Джа Хонг (Cha Tae Hyun), който е отведен от трима жътвари в отвъдния свят, под ръководството на Ганг Рим (Ha Jung Woo), водача на „Ангелите на смъртта“. Там Джа Хонг трябва да премине седем изпитания в продължение на 49 дни и да докаже, че е изживял правилно човешкия си живот. В това време неговите трима пазители го защитават, като неизбежно участват в човешките дела..."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"Istenek között: A két világ","runtime":140,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Példás életet élő tűzoltó Ja-Hong mentés közben elhunyt. Lelke átkel a túlvilágra, ahol a 49 napos barangolásnak indul. Ez idő alatt hét állomáson kerül ítélőszék elé. Ahol bizonyítania kell, hogy életét példásan élte. Amennyiben ez sikerül, esélyt kap az újjászületésre. Ebben három halál angyala lesz a segítségére, akik az útja és a perek során védelmezik. Gang Rim a halál angyalainak a vezetője, akit nem hagy hidegen az emberek sorsa. Hae Won Maek, aki az út biztonságáért felel. Duk-Choon, aki felkészül a tárgyalásokra és rendkívül érzelmes. Azonban a múlt homályai a küldetést a vártnál nehezebbé teszik. Az sem segít, hogy időközben Ja-Hong testvére Soo-Hong is eltávozik. Lelke azonban nem talál megnyugvást, amivel felbolygatja a másvilágot és veszélybe sodorja bátyja túlvilági végzete kimenetelét."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"Along with the Gods: The Two Worlds","runtime":139,"tagline":"O destino continua mesmo após a morte","homepage":"","overview":"Após morrer inesperadamente ao realizar um salvamento heróico, o jovem bombeiro Ja-hong é levado por três guardiões ao mundo espiritual, onde deverá passar por 7 julgamentos em um período de 49 dias. Os três guardiões foram designados para ajudá-lo em sua defesa, pois ele apenas terá permissão para reencarnar novamente na Terra se for considerado inocente em todos os julgamentos."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Along with the Gods: Los dos mundos","runtime":135,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Tras morir de forma inesperada, el bombero Ja-hong es llevado al más allá por tres guardianes. Sólo si pasa una serie de juicios durante y demuestra que es inocente en su vida, es apto para reencarnarse. Sus tres guardianes le apoyarán y le defenderán."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"與神同行","runtime":139,"tagline":"今世之後 來生之前","homepage":"","overview":"金自鴻 (車太鉉 飾) 是個正直、盡責的消防員，不幸在一次拯救任務中殉職。地獄使者「老大」江林 (河正宇 飾)、「護衞」解怨脈 (朱智勛 飾)、「助手」李德春 (金香起 飾) 奉命引領金自鴻到地府，接受七大地獄，七七四十九天的審判。唯有盡過七關的亡魂，方可轉世前託夢給在世的人。為了見年邁母親最後一面，金自鴻決心勇闖「背叛、暴力、不孝、殺戮、怠惰、欺騙、不義」七大地獄，與閻羅王 (李政宰 飾) 終極對峙…改編自大熱韓國同名網絡漫畫，帶你進入一個空前未見的神幻國度！"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Razem z bogami: Dwa światy","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Zgodnie z panującymi w zaświatach zasadami, każda dusza po śmierci musi przejść przez siedem prób w ciągu 49 dni. Reinkarnacji mogą dostąpić tylko te dusze, które przejdą pomyślnie wszelkie próby. Pewnego dnia do zaświatów trafia dusza Kim Ja Honga – strażaka, który zmarł na służbie."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"Junto a los Dioses: Los Dos Mundos","runtime":139,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Tras morir de forma inesperada, el bombero Ja-hong es llevado al más allá por tres guardianes. Sólo si pasa una serie de juicios y demuestra que es inocente en su vida, es apto para reencarnarse. Sus tres guardianes lo apoyarán y lo defenderán."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Entre Os Deuses - Os Dois Mundos","runtime":139,"tagline":"O destino continua mesmo após a morte.","homepage":"","overview":"Após morrer inesperadamente ao realizar um salvamento heróico, o jovem bombeiro Ja-hong é levado por três guardiões ao mundo espiritual, onde deverá passar por 7 julgamentos num período de 49 dias. Os três guardiões foram designados para ajudá-lo na sua defesa, pois ele apenas terá permissão para reencarnar se for considerado inocente em todos os julgamentos."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Kartu su dievais: Du pasauliai","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Tai istorija apie eilinio ugniagesio Kimo Jahongo mirtį ir vyriausiąjį grimą Gangrimą, kuris lydi jį į pomirtinį gyvenimą, kur atstovaus Jahongui septyniuose teismuose per 49 dienas, kuriuose bus aiškinamasi, kaip jis gyveno savo gyvenimą ir kur jis praleis visą likusią amžinybę."},"name":"Lietuvių","iso_639_1":"lt","iso_3166_1":"LT","english_name":"Lithuanian"},{"data":{"title":"Along With the Gods: The Two Worlds","runtime":139,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ja Hong is een doodnormale man die sterft. Kang Rim (\"De Engel des Doods\") is degene die Ja Hong vergezelt naar het hiernamaals. Hij krijgt de opdracht binnen 49 dagen 7 proeven te volbrengen."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"همراه با خدایان ۱: دو جهان","runtime":0,"tagline":"سرنوشت حتی پس از مرگ نیز ادامه دارد.","homepage":"","overview":"در خلاصه داستان این فیلم اکشن و فانتزی آمده است ، سه نگهبان از دنیایی دیگر مامور می‌شوند که یک آتش‌نشان فداکار را که قهرمانانه جان سپرده است ، به سوی زندگی پس از مرگ راهنمایی کنند. اما در این بین…"},"name":"فارسی","iso_639_1":"fa","iso_3166_1":"IR","english_name":"Persian"},{"data":{"title":"יחד עם האלים: שני העולמות","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"לאחר שמת בגבורה, כבאי מתלווה ל3 שומרים בעולם הבא בעקבות רוח מסתורית."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"Alături de zei: Cele două lumi","runtime":139,"tagline":"Soarta continuă chiar și după moarte.","homepage":"","overview":"După ce moare într-un mod neașteptat, Ja-hong este condus la viața de apoi de către trei “gardieni ai vieții”. Doar atunci când trece prin șapte încercări timp de 49 de zile și dovedește că este nevinovat în viața pe care tocmai a pierdut-o, el este capabil să se reîncarneze, iar cei trei tutori ai lui după moarte sunt alături de el pentru a-l apăra."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"Thử Thách Thần Chết: Giữa Hai Thế Giới","runtime":139,"tagline":"Khám phá thế giới chưa một ai biết đến.","homepage":"","overview":"Phim kể về hành trình phiêu lưu sau cái chết của một người đàn ông bình thường tên Ja Hong. Sứ giả được giao nhiệm vụ đến dẫn dắt Ja Hong về với Thế giới ngầm của Thần Chết Yeomra là Kang Rim, chính anh sẽ là người đưa Ja Hong đến 7 thử thách trong vòng 49 ngày trước khi đến gặp mặt đức vua Yeomra của mình. Cuộc hành trình sau cái chết này chính là bài khảo sát chính xác nhất cho Thần Chết Yeomra thấy được bản chất linh hồn của Ja Hong này và sẽ đưa ra quyết định “phán xét” cuối cùng cho anh."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"神と共に　第一章：罪と罰","runtime":140,"tagline":"K-POPグループEXOのメンバー、D.O.ことド・ギョンスが出演。チュ・ホミンによる人気ウェブコミックが原作の映画。","homepage":"","overview":"火災現場で殉職し、死後の世界へと足を踏み入れた消防士。そこで冥界の使者たちに導かれながら、7つの裁判を受けるため、過酷な地獄巡りに挑んでゆく。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"Along with the Gods: The Two Worlds","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":518068,"adult":false,"title":"Along with the Gods: The Last 49 Days","video":false,"overview":"As the deceased soul Ja-hong and his three afterlife guardians prepare for their remaining trials for reincarnation, the guardians soon come face to face with the truth of their tragic time on Earth 1,000 years earlier.","genre_ids":[28,12,14,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.1791,"vote_count":733,"poster_path":"/9BnqBHFGDv3WlCPB2qQwzAWdy7y.jpg","release_date":"2018-08-01","vote_average":8.045,"backdrop_path":"/ul4WiN9EJxsMokdg7z4Y6iisvHS.jpg","original_title":"신과함께-인과 연","original_language":"ko"},{"id":585831,"adult":false,"title":"The Bad Guys: Reign of Chaos","video":false,"overview":"A respectable village head decides to keep his son away from the violent politics of rural life. However, fate intervenes, forcing the young man to not only return home, but also take up the sickle.","genre_ids":[28,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.6235,"vote_count":161,"poster_path":"/on0F72EERa5nOSXaWKZhLfGrHQW.jpg","release_date":"2019-09-11","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/5ZXUijYxmB6lHWpWy2A36OCVrFu.jpg","original_title":"나쁜 녀석들: 더 무비","original_language":"ko"},{"id":517991,"adult":false,"title":"The Spy Gone North","video":false,"overview":"South Korea, 1993. An agent of the National Intelligence Service is sent to Beijing to infiltrate a group of North Korean officials with the ultimate goal of obtaining information about their nuclear program.","genre_ids":[18,36,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.7697,"vote_count":216,"poster_path":"/ib7SNOKqPKLyVXTjhuVJIglTC3E.jpg","release_date":"2018-08-08","vote_average":7.366,"backdrop_path":"/fReqenpUkU83y7rpEMscE5EjoDr.jpg","original_title":"공작","original_language":"ko"},{"id":291549,"adult":false,"title":"Assassination","video":false,"overview":"In Japanese-occupied Korea, three freedom fighters are assigned a mission to assassinate a genocidal military leader and his top collaborator. But the plan goes completely awry amidst double-crossings, counter-assassinations, and a shocking revelation about one of the assassins' past.","genre_ids":[28,53,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.8381,"vote_count":272,"poster_path":"/h4waWHgfIaqcFfMQ38aKDs6Pkw3.jpg","release_date":"2015-07-22","vote_average":7.305,"backdrop_path":"/mctcKx0Co9qe821DQuAjhoH33lw.jpg","original_title":"암살","original_language":"ko"},{"id":154030,"adult":false,"title":"The Tower","video":false,"overview":"Tower Sky, a luxurious building complex, has organised a lavish Christmas party for its VIP guests. However, things go awry when a fire breaks out and thousands of lives are endangered.","genre_ids":[28,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.1946,"vote_count":312,"poster_path":"/bt6OTuiq8ANbhIsOmZFztTw3Y2X.jpg","release_date":"2012-12-25","vote_average":6.976,"backdrop_path":"/f5LwI17I4F2QxJRw3JEUzfJ55Bh.jpg","original_title":"타워","original_language":"ko"},{"id":390497,"adult":false,"title":"Tunnel","video":false,"overview":"A man is on his way home when the poorly constructed tunnel he is driving through collapses, leaving him trapped leaving himself for the unexpected whilst emergency services struggle to help.","genre_ids":[53,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.6766,"vote_count":642,"poster_path":"/rLTYM8HeUo4YhgAlU888XEU8LMS.jpg","release_date":"2016-08-10","vote_average":7.295,"backdrop_path":"/37dC684Q6a4o83oAx8KEyNSuBV3.jpg","original_title":"터널","original_language":"ko"},{"id":492459,"adult":false,"title":"Dilan 1990","video":false,"overview":"At a Bandung high school, charming and rebellious Dilan vies for the affections of shy new student Milea.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6736,"vote_count":34,"poster_path":"/eitRZXfbw6rO0CfP3lPaGgK63qr.jpg","release_date":"2018-01-25","vote_average":7.7,"backdrop_path":"/2YiCk4kN24f29Uy6X7T9JktUmvn.jpg","original_title":"Dilan 1990","original_language":"id"},{"id":640882,"adult":false,"title":"3022","video":false,"overview":"A group of astronauts living in the haunting emptiness of deep space struggle to cope after Earth suffers an extinction-level event.","genre_ids":[878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.088,"vote_count":237,"poster_path":"/dp1brl24LXGFU3JPFaDoljDONRz.jpg","release_date":"2019-11-22","vote_average":5.249,"backdrop_path":"/ailBwpIwzUcNpuKSHtSwyqXAYCe.jpg","original_title":"3022","original_language":"en"},{"id":492998,"adult":false,"title":"Puzzle","video":false,"overview":"After years of caring exclusively for the needs of her husband and children, Agnes, a devoted housewife living in a small town near New York, has found something she really enjoys doing: solving puzzles.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.641,"vote_count":179,"poster_path":"/7CfijsjOsPKzz2Dd1zoMF5VPmZo.jpg","release_date":"2018-07-27","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/8lbj7ye0U60NU5BIjrQocO6ha75.jpg","original_title":"Puzzle","original_language":"en"},{"id":418588,"adult":false,"title":"Day of Reckoning","video":false,"overview":"Some years ago, the world experienced a \"day of reckoning\" when creatures came up from below and purged humanity of evil. Now, it is happening again.","genre_ids":[878,27,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.1142,"vote_count":74,"poster_path":"/lQOrFfaFTtSSmOtDCSM2EzHguOq.jpg","release_date":"2017-05-18","vote_average":4.9,"backdrop_path":"/yvcsAYA91dshyQvtHSEFcSxnMWl.jpg","original_title":"Day of Reckoning","original_language":"en"},{"id":792678,"adult":false,"title":"Cube","video":false,"overview":"Six complete strangers with widely varying personalities are involuntarily placed in an endless maze of interlocking cube-shaped rooms containing deadly traps.","genre_ids":[53,9648,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.4357,"vote_count":137,"poster_path":"/3uTnw1XahydeVkwFzY5xq5aFUh7.jpg","release_date":"2021-10-22","vote_average":5.3,"backdrop_path":"/wgbch1xH2OezrMKnol8Ze9UghPT.jpg","original_title":"CUBE 一度入ったら、最後","original_language":"ja"},{"id":729269,"adult":false,"title":"Sleeping with Danger","video":false,"overview":"Inspired by Ann Rule’s true crime collection Mortal Danger and Other True Cases. Paul Carter was like a knight in shining armor when he met flight attendant Grace Tanner and swept her into a passionate love affair. But her dream man quickly became her nightmare as his jealous rage ultimately led to a brutal attack. Incredibly, Grace was able to escape and go into hiding. Fearing for her life and the safety of other women Paul might seduce, Grace works with the police to bring Paul to justice.","genre_ids":[53,10770],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5127,"vote_count":50,"poster_path":"/78FSyBCA8BVAK3FsO1s6mTanRz7.jpg","release_date":"2020-08-01","vote_average":7.2,"backdrop_path":"/7z0QTuzxdUHkGISaYxtp0PVQmXp.jpg","original_title":"Sleeping with Danger","original_language":"en"},{"id":15412,"adult":false,"title":"Khosla Ka Ghosla!","video":false,"overview":"Kamal Khosla's land is grabbed by a land shark named Khurana. In a bid to retrieve their land, Khosla's elder son hatches a clever plan to con the crook and enlists the help of his friends and his dysfunctional family.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6485,"vote_count":112,"poster_path":"/nYcqtbv8Be6qpTcl6Y7qp0hvVdh.jpg","release_date":"2006-09-22","vote_average":7.254,"backdrop_path":"/mbB52rKxooyGM0k1EvLr15KPQJ5.jpg","original_title":"खोसला का घोसला","original_language":"hi"},{"id":480810,"adult":false,"title":"Shaadi Mein Zaroor Aana","video":false,"overview":"Satyendra aka Sattu and Aarti meet for a proposed arranged marriage and fall in love in the process. On the night of their marriage, an unexpected turn of events turns their world upside down. Set in the backdrop of India's civil services, Shaadi Mein Zaroor Aana explores the challenges that Satyendra and Aarti face as a middle-class couple in India.","genre_ids":[10749,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8176,"vote_count":82,"poster_path":"/hSpzMrohhzT7EQcvMIpXizP2hx4.jpg","release_date":"2017-11-10","vote_average":6.89,"backdrop_path":"/tywa9C2uE0zczo4OJcGkOser0pQ.jpg","original_title":"शादी में ज़रूर आना","original_language":"hi"},{"id":365719,"adult":false,"title":"The Witness","video":false,"overview":"A blind woman and a delivery boy attempt to solve a hit-and-run case the police have been unable to solve.","genre_ids":[80,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4948,"vote_count":51,"poster_path":"/xU22p0KtllkBTEYdAi9xM428SNa.jpg","release_date":"2015-10-30","vote_average":7.461,"backdrop_path":"/2nnJ03MYdXx2W3juIiYMLwHIK0q.jpg","original_title":"我是证人","original_language":"zh"},{"id":532327,"adult":false,"title":"How High 2","video":false,"overview":"When two jobless friends discover a hidden weed bible and the ultimate bud, they think that they’ve got it made…with 'seed' money to start a new snack delivery app. But, when nearly all of their stash and weed bible are stolen, the two potpreneurs set off on an outrageous, mind-bending adventure through Atlanta to find them. Stoned with supernatural powers, they search 'high' and low, stopping at nothing to recover their ticket to starting a legit business.","genre_ids":[35,10770],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8002,"vote_count":104,"poster_path":"/7eYIWzBQGdB955PnHyPxXrseXFK.jpg","release_date":"2019-08-24","vote_average":6.24,"backdrop_path":"/8tgjvsyiOh5s7foxvYl62m2y5RM.jpg","original_title":"How High 2","original_language":"en"},{"id":650036,"adult":false,"title":"The Rage","video":false,"overview":"An unprecedented epidemic of rabies is breaking out in the taiga. Infected wolves become more and more ferocious, and even the slightest bite brings certain death. At the same time, a desperate father decides to forcibly isolate his son in one of the hunting lodges in order to save him from addiction. Soon, he and several local residents will have to fight not only with a rabid pack, but also with the most dangerous predator of the forest.","genre_ids":[53,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.2426,"vote_count":40,"poster_path":"/kQ9TmxMDeWcRHlkbDLZvQ8xAGXh.jpg","release_date":"2023-04-24","vote_average":5.788,"backdrop_path":"/bxkAVrUQssmTbuXekqwMST492r9.jpg","original_title":"Бешенство","original_language":"ru"},{"id":300467,"adult":false,"title":"Dark Was the Night","video":false,"overview":"An evil is unleashed in a small town when a logging company sets up shop in the neighboring woods. Isolated and threatened, a mysterious force hidden within the trees outside the small town of Maiden Woods, strikes fear in the townspeople as Sheriff Paul Shields attempts to overcome the demons of his past while protecting those that he loves.","genre_ids":[27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5074,"vote_count":279,"poster_path":"/xSC7sWXbafOCa24itOHTpKXwOAV.jpg","release_date":"2014-10-17","vote_average":5.6,"backdrop_path":"/8111id3VJF3nKZ5z3Rf1Pca3OvY.jpg","original_title":"Dark Was the Night","original_language":"en"},{"id":12650,"adult":false,"title":"Il Mare","video":false,"overview":"In the year 1999, a young woman leaves her quaint seaside house and returns to the city, leaving in the mailbox a card for the next owner, with instructions to forward any mail of hers to the new address. In the year 1997, a jaded young architect moves into the same house and finds the letter. His reply, which he slips into the mailbox, finds its way to her, beginning a parallel-time love story separated by a span of two years.","genre_ids":[14,18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.9199,"vote_count":189,"poster_path":"/93A4yzQPQKV34XBECN8EsBzGlu0.jpg","release_date":"2000-09-09","vote_average":7.347,"backdrop_path":"/vd3jQVFeFo8pFlhKlZdHWyqmB4K.jpg","original_title":"시월애","original_language":"ko"},{"id":698860,"adult":false,"title":"MOTHER","video":false,"overview":"Shuhei is leading a tough life. His alcoholic mother Akiko can only hook up with bad guys and order Shuhei to go get money from his disapproving grandparents instead of going to school. Except raising the little half-sister, his rock-bottom life seems to have no end.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.0519,"vote_count":95,"poster_path":"/dpjTywNoMJ4VpQb9a7VYQ7Jqdkn.jpg","release_date":"2020-07-03","vote_average":7.005,"backdrop_path":"/x3JeJcqwl90v8qa6hfDHOEuOo8J.jpg","original_title":"MOTHER マザー","original_language":"ja"}],"similar_content":[{"id":8055,"adult":false,"title":"The Reader","video":false,"overview":"The story of Michael Berg, a German lawyer who, as a teenager in the late 1950s, had an affair with an older woman, Hanna, who then disappeared only to resurface years later as one of the defendants in a war crimes trial stemming from her actions as a concentration camp guard late in the war. He alone realizes that Hanna is illiterate and may be concealing that fact at the expense of her freedom.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":3.1528,"vote_count":3329,"poster_path":"/r0WURbmnhgKeBpHcpDULBgRedQM.jpg","release_date":"2008-12-10","vote_average":7.466,"backdrop_path":"/waMGsUEoHfYj3A1uRMUUgpBa71d.jpg","original_title":"The Reader","original_language":"en"},{"id":470968,"adult":false,"title":"At the Drive-In","video":false,"overview":"Unable to purchase a $50,000 digital projector, a group of film fanatics in rural Pennsylvania fight to keep a dying drive-in theater alive by screening only vintage 35mm film prints and working entirely for free.","genre_ids":[18,99,35],"popularity":0.1418,"vote_count":12,"poster_path":"/kMtyGXY9y3nnJpcwOXbI6SLpZYc.jpg","release_date":"2017-10-24","vote_average":7.3,"backdrop_path":"/cBpsVmRmBBE91iJ9iGgyfMpYHEh.jpg","original_title":"At the Drive-In","original_language":"en"},{"id":8536,"adult":false,"title":"Superman II","video":false,"overview":"Three Kryptonian criminals led by General Zod team up with Lex Luthor to conquer Earth, forcing a depowered Superman to regain his strength and stop them.","genre_ids":[878,28,12],"popularity":3.931,"vote_count":2467,"poster_path":"/3xk5cno9BHcnwc97XO9k21aI1Zi.jpg","release_date":"1980-12-12","vote_average":6.749,"backdrop_path":"/e77VeVcrXhxfCdJWD9rameYn7Qn.jpg","original_title":"Superman II","original_language":"en"},{"id":8285,"adult":false,"title":"The Spirit","video":false,"overview":"A Rookie cop named Denny Colt returns from the beyond as The Spirit, a hero whose mission is to fight against the bad forces from the shadows of Central City.  The Octopus, who kills anyone unfortunate enough to see his face, has other plans; he is going to wipe out the entire city.","genre_ids":[80,53,14,28],"popularity":1.3221,"vote_count":1046,"poster_path":"/g9qawfzR3LWRC8r8YZ9w2yaQi5W.jpg","release_date":"2008-12-25","vote_average":4.766,"backdrop_path":"/xqgSXgSIkTvyU9vfUcBOd6GYflJ.jpg","original_title":"The Spirit","original_language":"en"},{"id":8592,"adult":false,"title":"Dick Tracy","video":false,"overview":"The comic strip detective finds his life vastly complicated when Breathless Mahoney makes advances towards him while he is trying to battle Big Boy Caprice's united mob.","genre_ids":[12,35,80],"popularity":4.6454,"vote_count":1012,"poster_path":"/sjeP4bpgsUvAGE8oFcICy2GaHxw.jpg","release_date":"1990-04-05","vote_average":6.147,"backdrop_path":"/zkIMr5t0B95nZPhY4AvI4v3qYH.jpg","original_title":"Dick Tracy","original_language":"en"},{"id":8643,"adult":false,"title":"The Exorcism of Emily Rose","video":false,"overview":"When a younger girl called Emily Rose dies, everyone puts blame on the exorcism which was performed on her by Father Moore prior to her death. The priest is arrested on suspicion of murder. The trial begins with lawyer Erin Bruner representing Moore, but it is not going to be easy, as no one wants to believe what Father Moore says is true.","genre_ids":[80,18,27,53],"popularity":2.8981,"vote_count":2988,"poster_path":"/qMN0HIP34f736kkQcfvTfmL9TP3.jpg","release_date":"2005-09-09","vote_average":6.602,"backdrop_path":"/eHT36hVNslbJXCY3SXgtzxPE3cl.jpg","original_title":"The Exorcism of Emily Rose","original_language":"en"},{"id":8691,"adult":false,"title":"Cannibal Ferox","video":false,"overview":"Three friends out to disprove cannibalism meet two men on the run who tortured and enslaved a cannibal tribe to find emeralds, and now the tribe is out for revenge.","genre_ids":[12,27],"popularity":1.7706,"vote_count":262,"poster_path":"/ogvtVVsPSuzXKiQY1FCCKwIfBec.jpg","release_date":"1981-04-24","vote_average":5.37,"backdrop_path":"/bM5zSHNVyIdVxrMknkZUOfEJSUB.jpg","original_title":"Cannibal Ferox","original_language":"it"},{"id":8698,"adult":false,"title":"The League of Extraordinary Gentlemen","video":false,"overview":"To prevent a world war from breaking out, famous characters from Victorian literature band together to do battle against a cunning villain.","genre_ids":[14,28,53,878],"popularity":4.8741,"vote_count":4275,"poster_path":"/kdAuVFP63XXxnb983ry2pLCKd9S.jpg","release_date":"2003-07-11","vote_average":5.975,"backdrop_path":"/n3VpgjdOB1DkHSUe1DbFzV8ncpJ.jpg","original_title":"The League of Extraordinary Gentlemen","original_language":"en"},{"id":8393,"adult":false,"title":"The Gods Must Be Crazy","video":false,"overview":"A Coca-Cola bottle dropped from an airplane raises havoc among a normally peaceful tribe of African bushmen who believe it to be a utensil of the gods.","genre_ids":[28,35],"popularity":4.9138,"vote_count":1282,"poster_path":"/IgBfj5LfT7nwpodCZ34QCHp17x.jpg","release_date":"1980-09-10","vote_average":7.251,"backdrop_path":"/3gzI0UrLqIR9D40qshwduhGZCp3.jpg","original_title":"The Gods Must Be Crazy","original_language":"en"},{"id":277619,"adult":false,"title":"Sand Chronicles","video":false,"overview":"A young girl named Ann moves with her mother to her mother's hometown after her parents go through a divorce. There, Ann meets her first love Daigo Kitamura. Daigo helps her get used to life in the country. Ann even gets through her mother's suicide.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":0.268,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/jwMfgouNkNnP91lyDsfVgEHN74i.jpg","release_date":"2008-04-26","vote_average":6.3,"backdrop_path":"/8K5v38xlacCEdxPZQMFFEIFImhS.jpg","original_title":"砂時計","original_language":"ja"},{"id":8766,"adult":false,"title":"Hellraiser: Bloodline","video":false,"overview":"Three generations of the same family deal with the consequences of unleashing the forces of hell.","genre_ids":[27,878,53],"popularity":2.2521,"vote_count":598,"poster_path":"/tCQsVackQil2fl5TzOYrCAI6All.jpg","release_date":"1996-03-08","vote_average":5.285,"backdrop_path":"/8HFwBR7roggdQoFNbcVzR7tMfOY.jpg","original_title":"Hellraiser: Bloodline","original_language":"en"},{"id":1259102,"adult":false,"title":"Eternity","video":false,"overview":"In an afterlife where souls have one week to decide where to spend eternity, Joan is faced with the impossible choice between the man she spent her life with and her first love, who died young and has waited decades for her to arrive.","genre_ids":[10749,35,18],"popularity":18.2039,"vote_count":483,"poster_path":"/o8pg20G67BGmQvRkXwstNre062J.jpg","release_date":"2025-11-26","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/fuacZLpnohQtLD0AhtCErcPVL98.jpg","original_title":"Eternity","original_language":"en"},{"id":8831,"adult":false,"title":"Timecop","video":false,"overview":"In 2004, an officer for a security agency that regulates time travel must fend for his life against a shady politician who has a tie to his past.","genre_ids":[53,878,28,80],"popularity":2.6426,"vote_count":1275,"poster_path":"/bgxP6ws8ErBiarnb4S93vv0lkf4.jpg","release_date":"1994-09-15","vote_average":6.005,"backdrop_path":"/iNfDwioDBzqodomLbMfV8ZXj0yL.jpg","original_title":"Timecop","original_language":"en"},{"id":8839,"adult":false,"title":"Casper","video":false,"overview":"Casper is a kind young ghost who peacefully haunts a mansion in Maine. When specialist James Harvey arrives to communicate with Casper and his fellow spirits, he brings along his teenage daughter, Kat. Casper quickly falls in love with Kat, but their budding relationship is complicated not only by his transparent state, but also by his troublemaking apparition uncles and their mischievous antics.","genre_ids":[14,35,10751],"popularity":5.7829,"vote_count":4858,"poster_path":"/2ah8fNJFZVU3vcXhU5xfAYi2eym.jpg","release_date":"1995-05-26","vote_average":6.3,"backdrop_path":"/sQPckU0TfSeYIlUneHfIXwzQC2f.jpg","original_title":"Casper","original_language":"en"},{"id":8967,"adult":false,"title":"The Tree of Life","video":false,"overview":"The impressionistic story of a Texas family in the 1950s. The film follows the life journey of the eldest son, Jack, through the innocence of childhood to his disillusioned adult years as he tries to reconcile a complicated relationship with his father. Jack finds himself a lost soul in the modern world, seeking answers to the origins and meaning of life while questioning the existence of faith.","genre_ids":[18,14],"popularity":2.946,"vote_count":3278,"poster_path":"/l8cwuB5WJSoj4uMAsnzuHBOMaSJ.jpg","release_date":"2011-05-17","vote_average":6.727,"backdrop_path":"/xq1HIwZq9VbuvMQELAua1nqEkH.jpg","original_title":"The Tree of Life","original_language":"en"},{"id":8976,"adult":false,"title":"A Lot Like Love","video":false,"overview":"On a flight from Los Angeles to New York, Oliver and Emily make a connection, only to decide that they are poorly suited to be together. Over the next seven years, however, they are reunited time and time again, they go from being acquaintances to close friends to... lovers?","genre_ids":[35,18,10749],"popularity":2.1538,"vote_count":1344,"poster_path":"/6xrF9zwEbYiYBOalMO14RAWBLLj.jpg","release_date":"2005-04-21","vote_average":6.827,"backdrop_path":"/kRpzc3knsyOzLFOi4C4ZUbLPScu.jpg","original_title":"A Lot Like Love","original_language":"en"},{"id":8980,"adult":false,"title":"Mortadelo & Filemon: The Big Adventure","video":false,"overview":"In the Headquarters of the T.I.A. (Terminal Intelligence Agency), someone has stolen Professor Bacterio's most dangerous invention, the D.O.T. (Demoralizer of Troops), an artifact that ends up in the hands of a very short, wacky dictator who is ready to use it for criminal purposes. The T.I.A Chief, though, is firm in his resolve: if he wants to get the D.O.T. back, he must NOT count on his agents Mortadelo & Filemon. But when the crime fighting duo discover that the T.I.A. has engaged a cocky and slimy detective from outside the agency, they decide to act at their own risk, even if that risk involves all of Humanity.","genre_ids":[28,35],"popularity":0.4255,"vote_count":138,"poster_path":"/tiP17WpKYLotQwg4EUs0UfmQq24.jpg","release_date":"2003-02-07","vote_average":5.638,"backdrop_path":"/gLIDdvf3vmYmZ9RPzEfGUKQqbDO.jpg","original_title":"La gran aventura de Mortadelo y Filemón","original_language":"es"},{"id":8850,"adult":false,"title":"The Shadow","video":false,"overview":"Based on the 1930s comic strip, The Shadow is put up against his archenemy Shiwan Khan, who plans to take over the world by holding a city to ransom using an atom bomb. Using his powers of invisibility and \"the power to cloud men's minds\", The Shadow comes blazing to the rescue with explosive results.","genre_ids":[14,28,80],"popularity":1.8995,"vote_count":554,"poster_path":"/xAbFJH3vQYZvUyzzGAtG4OLy492.jpg","release_date":"1994-07-01","vote_average":6.073,"backdrop_path":"/j3CMtQbRS4bBAuRuoTBpnPAaHSj.jpg","original_title":"The Shadow","original_language":"en"},{"id":8854,"adult":false,"title":"Steel","video":false,"overview":"When a renegade military reject puts new superweapons in dangerous hands, John Henry Irons becomes Steel. Wearing body armor, wielding a fearsome electrohammer and riding a gadget-packed motorcycle, he's ready to wage war... if he can fix the untimely glitches in his untested gear.","genre_ids":[878,28,80,14],"popularity":2.4995,"vote_count":272,"poster_path":"/ufA7d5LT2rGj58KaZErPhcMkJ4U.jpg","release_date":"1997-08-15","vote_average":4.283,"backdrop_path":"/61Wj1C1hrOyu6mAHARS8J5ShOzq.jpg","original_title":"Steel","original_language":"en"},{"id":8867,"adult":false,"title":"The Punisher","video":false,"overview":"The avenging angel of Marvel Comics fame comes brilliantly to life in this searing action-adventure thriller! Dolph Lundgren stars as Frank Castle, a veteran cop who loses his entire family to a mafia car bomb. His ex-partner believes Castle survived the blast and became the Punisher, living in the sewers and exacting vigilante violence against mob bosses throughout the city. When the populace is caught in the midst of a gang war that he caused, Castle must again emerge from the shadows and save the innocent.","genre_ids":[28,80,18,53],"popularity":2.1304,"vote_count":653,"poster_path":"/tA0O0hYyHX7Hl2Fl8VEtGtfBtjI.jpg","release_date":"1989-10-05","vote_average":5.768,"backdrop_path":"/tFmrdnfXM0p6ihMTFpptYOKEfSl.jpg","original_title":"The Punisher","original_language":"en"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt7160070","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":"Q26252639","instagram_id":null,"metacritic_id":"movie/along-with-the-gods-the-two-worlds","mydramalist_id":"308365","rotten_tomatoes_id":"m/along_with_the_gods_the_two_worlds"},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":nul